snippet.title: Santa Claus In Trouble - DOWNLOAD + GAMEPLAY (No Commentary)
snippet.description:
This video of Santa Claus In Trouble shows the gameplay without commentary. In this game you have to control Santa Claus through very difficult jumping levels. It's not easy.
